<p><a name="Buddhism" id="Buddhism"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Moksha&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5" title="Edit section: Buddhism">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Buddhism</span></h2>
<div class="rellink noprint relarticle mainarticle">Main article: <a href="/wiki/Nirvana" title="Nirvana">Nirvana</a></div>
<p>In <a href="/wiki/Buddhism" title="Buddhism">Buddhism</a> the concept of liberation is <a href="/wiki/Nirvana" title="Nirvana">Nirvana</a>. It is referred to as "the highest happiness" and is the goal of the Buddhist path.</p>
<p><a name="Jainism" id="Jainism"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Moksha&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6" title="Edit section: Jainism">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Jainism</span></h2>
